description: Directly and carefully observe the main lamp and the internal indicator lamp (through the peephole) in the real system, in a darkened environment, over several minutes. Verify with your own eyes whether either lamp actually turns off or noticeably dims every ~20 seconds for ~0.5 s, or whether both remain continuously lit with no fluctuation despite any simulation or prior reports., outcome='The main load lamp and the internal indicator lamp are both lit and show no observable internal faults.  \nNo peephole operations were performed, as the Load Cube does not support opening or closing a peephole.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.', precise_action_cost=35.0, cost_breakdown=[('open_peephole', 5.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('open_inspection_panel', 5.0), ('observe_component', 10.0), ('close_peephole', 5.0)], simplified_outcome=None), DiagnosticActionResult(action=
name: Test -> control module – internal ground/reference and negative I/O wiring continuity,
description: Perform a continuity test (or low‑ohms resistance check) between the control module’s internal ground node, its negative I/O terminals (input − and output −), and the negative terminals of the relay coil and comparator/sensor network to confirm that all these nodes are truly common and solidly connected, with no intermittent or high‑resistance joint that could sporadically shift reference potentials and create a perceived 20‑s oscillation without visible relay or lamp changes., outcome='Continuity and resistance measurements for the Control Input Cable (−), Control Output Cable (−), Control Relay, and Sensor Bias Resistor are all nominal and match their respective expected values. The inspection panel for the control module has been successfully opened for internal access.\nCurrent persistent circuit state [differences with the starting state]:\nNo circuit-level changes introduced by diagnostics.', precise_action_cost=85.0, cost_breakdown=[('test_continuity', 20.0), ('test_continuity', 20.0), ('open_inspection_panel', 5.0), ('test_continuity', 20.0), ('test_continuity', 20.0)], simplified_outcome=None)] 
